               class="btn btn-amber btn-lg">
              Book a Free 30-Min Call <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:hello@yarova.ca" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg ghost-light">Email us instead</a>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-contact">
            <span>WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/16047197918" target="_blank" rel="noopener">+1 (604) 719-7918</a> &middot; Mon&ndash;Fri 9:00&ndash;18:00 PT</span>
            <span>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@yarova.ca">hello@yarova.ca</a></span>
